column6: RBH Industrie manufactures automobiles. The company was founded in 2004 in France.

Workz Group designs and develops mobile solutions and serialisation software. Its secure connected solutions include eSIM, OTA remote provisioning, operating systems, managed chip security, and VAS. The company manufactures SIM cards; scratch cards; packaging solutions; and customised printed products such as tickets, cards, labels, and tags. In addition, it provides FIATA-certified logistics, artwork design, data management, SIM training, and technical support services. The company partners with Ethio Telecom, Orange, Econet, Telenor, Vodafone, Batelco, and Etisalat. Workz Group was founded in 1997 and as of November 2018, is based in Dublin, Ireland.

NEC engages in IT services, platform, carrier network, social infrastructure, and personal solution activities worldwide. Its IT services segment offers consulting, integration, and support services. The personal solutions segment oversees personal computers, monitors, mobile handsets, and Internet service. The carrier network supplies network infrastructure equipment for telecom carriers. The platform business supplies network systems such as servers, supercomputers, storage equipment, and IP telephony systems, while the social infrastructure segment provides broadcasting systems, satellites, CCTV surveillance, and other security systems. NEC was established in 1899 and is based in Tokyo, Japan.

Orange provides a range of fixed telephony and mobile telecommunications, data transmission, Internet and multimedia, and other value-added services to consumers, businesses, and other telecommunications operators under the Orange brand worldwide. The company was formerly known as France Telecom and changed its name to Orange in July 2013. The company was founded in 1990 and is based in Paris, France.
France-based KeyOpsTech provides a platform which digitises the tracking of mail deliveries. It was founded in 2017 and is based in Lyon, France.

Sika is a speciality chemical company which develops and manufactures products for the construction industry. The company focuses on the production of systems and products for bonding, sealing, damping, reinforcing and protecting in the building and the motor vehicle industries. The company was established in 1910 and is headquartered in Baar, Switzerland.
column36: Ivo Schaedler, regional manager of Europe, Middle East and Africa said: "Senegal is one of the fastest growing west African countries, and we are gaining an early foothold in these growth markets."

column6: US-based Elahi Enterprises Inc was founded in 2003 in Plano, Texas. The company's line of business includes preparing advertising and placing such advertising in periodicals, newspapers, radio and television, and other media outlets. Elahi has three subsidiaries, including Akorbi, a provider of multilingual enterprise solutions.

Partech Ventures is a private equity and venture capital firm specialising in seed, startup, late venture, early, buyouts, mid venture, later stage, emerging growth, bridge financing, and growth capital investments. The company was founded in 1982 and is based in Paris, France.
Baloon Assurance provides an online platform which allows users to compare and buy insurance. The company was founded in 2017 and is based in Paris, France.
